The paper deals with computer vision-based sign language recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The focus of the paper is on human pose estimation, which is a task related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions hand detection, which is a task related to object detection (cs.CV). The methods used in the paper are based on deep learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper introduces a new dataset, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
